Instead of increasing damage - I think a shorter cast time - mid damaged lure would be more appropriate.  Of course thats just more appropriate for PvP and not PvE which means it won't ever be done <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
