raise int soft cap to 255. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uscabrous2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Scabrous2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(11/10/01 3:56:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Whats the purpose of the 66% nerf</span><hr size=1> Has anyone ever done a listing of spell damage with nerf?<br>
